tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MaintenanceSchedules (
    maintenance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    system_name VARCHAR(100),
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    technician_name VARCHAR(100),
    labor_hours FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE maintenance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    schedule_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(100),
    technician_name VARCHAR(255),
    work_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (schedule_id) REFERENCES maintenance_schedule(schedule_id)
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_record (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    maintenance_id INT,
    technician_id INT,
    status VARCHAR(50),
    completion_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceSchedules (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    building_system_id INT,
    scheduled_maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (building_system_id) REFERENCES BuildingSystems(building_system_id)
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceRecords (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    schedule_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    technician_name VARCHAR(255),
    maintenance_notes TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (schedule_id) REFERENCES MaintenanceSchedules(schedule_id)
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_records (
    record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    schedule_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    completion_date DATE,
    technician_name VARCHAR(100)
);
